          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Article I Amicus and Intervention Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill provides additional statutory authority for Congress to participate in judicial proceedings involving the constitutionality of a federal law.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-10-16T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
